cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.DC, cs.DS, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and word embeddings. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) as word2vec is a widely used machine learning algorithm. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) as the paper discusses techniques for distributing word2vec computation across nodes in a compute cluster. It could also be categorized under cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) as the paper proposes a new algorithm for word2vec that improves reuse of various data structures. Finally, it could be categorized under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as word2vec is a neural network-based algorithm.
